---
title: Caribbean Beef Meatballs & Cheesy Fries with Smokey Aioli & Corn Slaw
description: Charred corn is the perfect addition to a colourful slaw, it's juicy and sweet. Keep tastiness going by spicing the beef
meatballs in a Caribbean jerk seasoning. If that’s still not enough for you, we’re positive the cheesy fries will propel
you to the finish line.
